<p><date when="1830-08-30">Augt. 30 1830</date></p>
<p><persName>Mr E. R. Wighman</persName></p>

<p><persName>Mr Weigh[t]man</persName> It being out of my Power to go down to see
you survey my <placeName>Land </placeName>at this time If you have not done it I wish you
to write me imediately and perhaps I will be able to come down&#8212;
If you should be surveying at this time I wish you to doe it to the
best advantage for me   Yours</p>

<p><persName>Benjn T Jaques</persName></p>

<p><date when="1830-09-07">Sept 7th 1830</date></p>



        </div1>
